data.description:
Ready to make your home nestled among the mountains of Unicoi County? This home may be perfect for you!

A split bedroom floor plan with open concept kitchen, living and dining in the middle is just what you need.

The large deck is perfect for entertaining or enjoying your morning coffee in the peace and quiet. 

Both outbuildings will convey with the property.

Buyer/Buyer's Agent to verify all information.
